      • actuallyWrite

        public void actuallyWrite(OutputConfiguration configuration,
                 Intern input,
                 java.io.PrintWriter writer)
        Converts the input to CSV and writes it to the file that the PrintWriter has already opened. If the data shall be appended, it does not write the header again, but only the data records.
